# OpenSkills Environment Variables
# Get your token at: https://6551.io/mcp

# Unified token for all skills (news, twitter, trading)
OPEN_TOKEN=your-token-here

# Note: You can also store your token in a config file:
# - macOS/Linux: ~/.config/openskills/credentials.json
# - Windows: %APPDATA%\openskills\credentials.json
# Format: {"token": "your-token-here"}
# Priority: Environment variable > Config file
